      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. Every detail reflects a commitment to preservation, offering the discerning collector or enthusiast a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example of engineering excellence. We invite private viewings for those who demand nothing short of perfection.",
