    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty to believe it. It's in absolute mint condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for this to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
