      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This 2002 BMW M3 (E46) is an exceptional specimen of high-revving atmospheric engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a flawlessly maintained VANOS variable valve timing system. This example features a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is in peerless condition, with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that remains tight and responsive. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been scrutinized to ensure peak performance. Finished in a deep luster with an immaculate interior, this M3 represents a turn-key opportunity for the purist seeking a definitive analog driving experience.",
